{"tid":2410004,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日去拜pair新婚夫婦, 夠膽死話唔派利是","createTime":"2021-02-16T09:15:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T23:31:13.000Z","uid":127425,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"852059f07a85410ca7945731c26121fb97d74d85","tid":2410004,"uid":127425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T09:15:25.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n今日我地成班朋友去佢地屋企拜年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地同佢地都算friend過打band<br />\n佢地結婚我地都有去做兄弟<br />\n前幾日就邀請我地去佢地新入伙屋企過年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我地都好識做, 買左好多野上去賀佢新屋入伙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一開頭都無乜野, 不過終於有條友忍唔住問左果兩公婆<br />\n&quot;結左婚, 大個啦喎, 要開始派利是啦喎&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地都好醒目, 一聽就知係問緊佢地拎利是<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes1000.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes1000.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知個老婆話(認真mode), &quot;下, 你地大過我地喎, 正常都係你地比我地啦&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (我地90後)<br />\n佢講完之後dead air左差唔多半分鐘<br />\n跟住有條友話醒起有野做要走先, 有幾個都跟左佢走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我仲聽到有人話車錢都蝕埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n發覺而家D後生真係唔識做<br />\n結左婚派利是是常識吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0d42694e2254d7b468116a27c8e41d69ab4bfd2","tid":2410004,"uid":378917,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T09:33:23.000Z","msg":"唔知真心定假膠<br />\n但我覺得正常結婚係要派<br />\n其實新年既野求個意頭 <br />\n派果個有人拜下年幾開心 <br />\n細封啲冇所謂 利是係想要個祝福既意思<br />\n但唔撚比又好似孤寒左啲 好撚肉酸<br />\n就算雙封派十幾人 比盡幾百蚊 唔洗死下話"},{"pid":"24237f988a14a4a39fa175e07136e18099e6f9fa","tid":2410004,"uid":236891,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T09:37:53.000Z","msg":"我當利是係一份你對我既認同，同事嚟計，上一年同你合作咗咁耐你廿蚊都唔想比我，都幾hard feel<br />\n<br />\n其實20蚊真係早餐都唔夠比，少少心意都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6866896b52e5fcac9875f90941e24eea035f6e88","tid":2410004,"uid":127425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b0d42694e2254d7b468116a27c8e41d69ab4bfd2","tid":2410004,"uid":378917,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T09:33:23.000Z","msg":"唔知真心定假膠<br />\n但我覺得正常結婚係要派<br />\n其實新年既野求個意頭 <br />\n派果個有人拜下年幾開心 <br />\n細封啲冇所謂 利是係想要個祝福既意思<br />\n但唔撚比又好似孤寒左啲 好撚肉酸<br />\n就算雙封派十幾人 比盡幾百蚊 唔洗死下話"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T09:39:29.000Z","msg":"佢地兩公婆覺得利是係大人比細路<br />\n所以就算結左婚都唔駛派比D年紀大過佢地既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ecc7648d935b8e438e128e0ed63b272bb876a82","tid":2410004,"uid":342903,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T09:40:15.000Z","msg":"唔想派就唔好新年約朋友啦"},{"pid":"0008984e3bf771212ecca6b4b17826e012d5a41b","tid":2410004,"uid":127425,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"24237f988a14a4a39fa175e07136e18099e6f9fa","tid":2410004,"uid":236891,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T09:37:53.000Z","msg":"我當利是係一份你對我既認同，同事嚟計，上一年同你合作咗咁耐你廿蚊都唔想比我，都幾hard feel<br />\n<br />\n其實20蚊真係早餐都唔夠比，少少心意都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T09:40:32.000Z","msg":"真係<br />\n都唔諗住你封$50<br />\n$10都冇真係過分左<br />\n好心淡囉"},{"pid":"7c9e5eaed65ae3b34fae367278804739003678be","tid":2410004,"uid":357065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T09:41:51.000Z","msg":"唔好話後生 <br />\n上左年紀都有試過唔